<Content_wSideColumn ID="x58743" Name="NewActivity" Layout="byuidefault.xsl"><Title type="string" label="Title" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Sumbit a New Idea for Student Activities</Title><Abstract type="string" label="Abstract" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">For BYU-I students who want to suggest their own activity</Abstract><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="SideColumn" label="L/R Column" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"><MoveLeft type="boolean" label="Toggle column right or left (right is default)" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</MoveLeft><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="ImageComponent" label="Image Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="LeftColumnImageComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="TextComponent" label="Text Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="ColumnTextComponent" Expanded="false"/><fbookTop type="boolean" label="Put facebook at top of page" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</fbookTop><fbookStatus type="string" label="Facebook ID#" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"></fbookStatus><fbookToken type="string" label="Access_Token" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"></fbookToken><fbookDisplayed type="string" label="Number of facebook messages to display" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">1</fbookDisplayed></xPower><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<div>
<p><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="color: #993366;"><strong>Have a great idea? </strong></span><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino; color: #333399; font-size: large;"><strong>Make it a reality.</strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino; font-size: small;">BYU-Idaho encourages students to explore ideas for new activities.&nbsp; In fact, every aspect of Student Activities is run by student leaders.&nbsp; The following information outlines how to get your new activity approved and implemented on campus.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino; font-size: small;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Step #1:&nbsp; Sharing your idea</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino; font-size: small;">To do this you will propose your idea though the online application below.<br /></span><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino; font-size: small;">If you would like help writing your proposal you can contact a student leader or advisor.<br /></span><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino; font-size: small;">Once you submit your proposal it will go to the appropriate student leader or advisor for review.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino; font-size: small;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Step #2:&nbsp; Present</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino; font-size: small;">After initial review the student leader or advisor may invite you to present your idea to the Student Activities Council.<br /></span><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino; font-size: small;">The Student Activities Council will hear your proposal and address any concerns.&nbsp; If your idea is not approved you will need to modify it and present it to the council again.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino; font-size: small;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Step #3:&nbsp; Implement</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino; font-size: small;">Once your idea is approved the real work begins.&nbsp; You will then work with student leaders to implement your idea.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino; font-size: small;">Congratulations!</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: large;"><strong><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino;">Ready to begin? </span></strong></span><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino; font-size: small;"><a href="https://byui.qualtrics.com/SE/?SID=SV_0ptudEis5ZO91Pe" target="_blank">Sumbit your New Idea here!</a></span></p>
